{"tid":378832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先令屋企人濕疹好返","createTime":"2017-08-28T18:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T07:48:25.000Z","uid":615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af2cb0287f3b978db8c5233c7e45c06e39ec6bd7","tid":378832,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"已經變左月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半夜聽到老母走去沖涼<br />\n見到佢件衫染滿血跡<br />\n真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩方法都試晒<br />\n海鹽都買過兩盒，無效<br />\n<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0ccbf4210724a1101df250a5c1562faa8b2fd8","tid":378832,"uid":104038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經變左月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半夜聽到老母走去沖涼<br />\n見到佢件衫染滿血跡<br />\n真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩方法都試晒<br />\n海鹽都買過兩盒，無效<br />\n<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無試過去做敏感test？ <br />\n聽講有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6221bd5ce09fa51fa4b647d7d6cc5203d946ad","tid":378832,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:42:49.000Z","msg":"有冇睇過皮膚科?"},{"pid":"636fdd5ed7dd0c54c6b82940b7ad1d18e59160e6","tid":378832,"uid":121053,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"要戒口唔可以食濕毒野<br />\n同埋睇醫生啦ching<br />\n沖涼液都要轉 之前用施巴ok"},{"pid":"32faa97f1d6c719e0cf5e31d71dafb4f007026b7","tid":378832,"uid":35698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"平時會點護理?<br />\n有無試過戒口?<br />\n沖涼沖偏凍既水，總之唔好沖熱水<br />\n唔好用沖涼液，轉用皂（最好搵啲咩成份天然嗰啲）<br />\n我自己唔係勁嚴重，沖完涼係噴死海鹽水上去，等佢乾就搽cream<br />\n咩cream好呢? 平既就aq, 想用好啲既就cetaxxxx / phyxxxgel  (其實我唔識串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 呢兩個牌子都係醫生介紹<br />\n我咁樣做都有時會痕，但我覺得算係under control 了"},{"pid":"98ca8f499b80de05d391a337b444b85ba340ef4e","tid":378832,"uid":128114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經變左月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半夜聽到老母走去沖涼<br />\n見到佢件衫染滿血跡<br />\n真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩方法都試晒<br />\n海鹽都買過兩盒，無效<br />\n<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有傷口唔好用海鹽呀<br />\n無臭味用清水就夠喇<br />\n俾啲心機日日搽cream <br />\nLup都要搽 最多開大啲冷氣"},{"pid":"9043632da9c3ad9f5de55c74359214abbb8f8200","tid":378832,"uid":73563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:54:34.000Z","msg":"用正常（無加熱水）水喉水沖涼已經有好大幫助"},{"pid":"078b0e55b56ff1817e3975c622af53e6d794f5ae","tid":378832,"uid":128114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經變左月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半夜聽到老母走去沖涼<br />\n見到佢件衫染滿血跡<br />\n真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩方法都試晒<br />\n海鹽都買過兩盒，無效<br />\n<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有傷口唔好用海鹽呀<br />\n無臭味用清水就夠喇<br />\n俾啲心機日日搽cream <br />\nLup都要搽 最多開大啲冷氣</blockquote><br />\n好嚴重個時要搽有小小類固醇藥膏 唔嚴重就搽cream <br />\n揀啲cream 易吸收既 (唔一定貴好)搽多幾次"},{"pid":"29bc3a303d815b51d7b4a044ca5ad96f2481d3bd","tid":378832,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"多謝你地咁有心機覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\naq cream，類固醇etc ，一痕已經搽<br />\n敏感藥都有食開(醫生處方)<br />\n基本上所有要做既都有做<br />\n可能我媽咪見無乜效就放棄<br />\n我有買過手工梘俾佢用，不過用用下淨係返凍水沖涼<br />\n<br />\n我唔知濕疹究竟有幾痕幾痕<br />\nr到皮膚損晒好似變左病態咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803916feb245a50d0058d4fbecc2526c59b4ed2b","tid":378832,"uid":47946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:05:51.000Z","msg":"男朋友之前都算嚴重，睇左大埔一個醫生之後斷尾<br />\n大埔昌運中心鄭明俊，希望幫到你同你屋企人<br />\nTel:<br />\n2663 0221<br />\n地址:<br />\n安慈路4號昌運中心商場1樓108A1舖<br />\n專業資格:<br />\n香港大學內外全科醫學士 1999<br />\n倫敦皇家兒科文憑 2004<br />\n倫敦大學皮膚學碩士 2004<br />\n倫敦藥劑師會生殖泌尿科文憑 2004<br />\n提供醫療程序及手術:<br />\nMedical Check Up <br />\nDermatology Consultations <br />\nVaccination <br />\nInsurance Claims <br />\nGenitourinary Consultations<br />\nExcision of Skin Tags <br />\nWarts Cryotherapy <br />\nBotox Injection <br />\nWound Management <br />\nScar Management<br />\n其他資料:<br />\n收費:<br />\n$120以上<br />\n皮膚科診症$280<br />\n診症時間:<br />\n星期一 ︰ 0900-2030 <br />\n星期二 ︰ 0900-2030 <br />\n星期三 ︰ 0900-2030 <br />\n星期四 ︰ 0900-2030 <br />\n星期五 ︰ 0900-2030 <br />\n星期六 ︰ 0900-2030 <br />\n星期日 ︰ 0900-1930 <br />\n公眾假期 ︰ 0900-1930"},{"pid":"bbe92c8a7dadea1e7ef62f88f9f49385cd99dec1","tid":378832,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"#10 太長唔quote了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx先<br />\n但睇醫生係咪都係視乎佢開既藥令濕疹唔好再發咁？"},{"pid":"377548356745ee3978270d00c431dddb1211f851","tid":378832,"uid":94444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:11:49.000Z","msg":"我最近濕疹都反發 食左藥都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1be4cf9052c942feb84eb04924fd05b4bfe668","tid":378832,"uid":47946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#10 太長唔quote了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx先<br />\n但睇醫生係咪都係視乎佢開既藥令濕疹唔好再發咁？</blockquote><br />\n其實我都唔多明原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但果陣佢開左藥膏，搽晒之後就無事<br />\n再想翻發嘅時候，忍手唔R同勤清潔就無菌無事<br />\n直頭無特登用凍水沖涼之類"},{"pid":"95cb52880d435593d55a419450111be2790af932","tid":378832,"uid":139724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:42:03.000Z","msg":"濕疹良藥<br />\n金銀花 煲水飲 敷身體 都得<br />\n我濕疹都係靠佢好"},{"pid":"aa5ef0571c5feb87cac86a1e4a938f13e7a65cb1","tid":378832,"uid":139724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:43:06.000Z","msg":"最好唔好用咁多類固醇藥物啦 對身體好傷<br />\n病向淺中醫"},{"pid":"f3f1a7e9cf3f1fd4bba44ec41009f367606ddc86","tid":378832,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:47:13.000Z","msg":"唔知堅唔堅但聽人講睇中醫有用"},{"pid":"86a3937a6da0f13cc2d5b5574806c46a83942da7","tid":378832,"uid":121012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T20:28:19.000Z","msg":"自己都好嚴重，可以講嚴重過伯母<br />\n飲咗中藥連續好幾個月加介口好咗6/ 7 成<br />\n可能自己敏感體質，好易無啦啦又發翻<br />\n但中醫真係咁多年黎最有效<br />\n皮膚摸落去熱係你有內熱，平時食埋嘅野個脾胃消化得唔好d 毒就積積埋埋，排唔到就積埋做濕<br />\n所以最好就係睇中醫由內清走d 毒咁佢就唔會發岀黎做濕疹<br />\n<br />\n西醫短期係有用，但身體嘅熱毒仲會喺度，只係幫到你一時三刻，所以中西合璧啦<br />\n<br />\n我都明好辛苦好痕，所以用住類固醇cream 再日日飲苦茶再介口，真心好唔得曬一定好一半有多<br />\n<br />\n針灸都work 如果budget 許可，因為都要針好一斷時間<br />\n<br />\n利申: 由細到大都係咁，中醫d 野我唔係pro 但咁多年睇醫生聽聽埋埋，點都好希望幫到你! 記得一定要介口，唔介點睇中醫都無用"},{"pid":"7a55330e4520b34cae8837597d3480fdea2f12fc","tid":378832,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T20:35:59.000Z","msg":"介口能醫百病"},{"pid":"9570e40ef6cd5cd6eddcdc9c06ff5449980ed0e1","tid":378832,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:18:31.000Z","msg":"搽藥膏 薄薄地搽 三兩日先搽一次<br />\n介凍飲"},{"pid":"27043f98db4c2ba1a67a2de5b2099dd316fe5d1f","tid":378832,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:33:28.000Z","msg":"洗少少錢去做敏感測試，睇下對啲咩過敏<br />\netc貓狗/塵蟎/食物/物質<br />\n之前有個post既巴打對鐵敏感唔掂得鐵<br />\n所以最好去check check個致敏源係邊<br />\n咁先長遠解決到問題"},{"pid":"e056c2688ee2c202e49f32eab5cee672c4b82807","tid":378832,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T22:58:43.000Z","msg":"唔該曬各位巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有勸過佢唔好飲凍嘢 keep左一排又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中醫都有睇過， 斷左尾一排貶下眼又返發<br />\n<br />\n睇黎去驗血最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打可以介紹下邊間診所<br />\n啱啱google完，過敏病及哮喘診療中心 呢間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef236a8f0d86fe8d215d8fa10ff6c0389b45fcd","tid":378832,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T23:03:37.000Z","msg":"有得好架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c26411c1d7004c3a415026f20e4cd9667436df","tid":378832,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T23:13:39.000Z","msg":"試下羅漢果煲水飲 我屋企日日煲日日飲 好左好多<br />\n利申:以前都好嚴重 依家戒口唔食牛 飲羅漢果水"},{"pid":"79c76de8878c6f68e1e9ca274f746fb9cc59f1c8","tid":378832,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下羅漢果煲水飲 我屋企日日煲日日飲 好左好多<br />\n利申:以前都好嚴重 依家戒口唔食牛 飲羅漢果水</blockquote><br />\n我有聽過<br />\n究竟羅漢果有d咩可以令濕疹好"},{"pid":"2c684fb1005868b69b6a9d1a7fddf1f937090c91","tid":378832,"uid":61313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:27:40.000Z","msg":"濕疹唔好搽類固醇，短時間會消退但之後會更嚴重。三年前塊面有濕疹，一發起來會流黃色液體，痕到仆街，平時都係粉紅色一粒粒係面，好核突。最初睇西醫搽類固醇以為有效，點知時間一長發現唔對路。後來係睇中醫，戒口同飲佐八個月中藥，醫生另外開佐包藥煲水洗面，而家斷晒尾，醫個時真係好撚辛苦，又唔可以戴口罩焗住，俾同學笑到抬唔起頭。"}]}